			<p><b>Anthropologie Internship</b></p>
			<p><i>Designing an Unimagined Experience</i></p>
			<p><b>Date</b> 2011<br/>
			<b>Location</b> Internship in Philadelphia<br/>
			<b>Size</b> Varies by project<br/></p>
				
			<p>The following projects are selections from work completed during my summer internship with Anthropologie Store Design. I assisted on designs for Anthropologie, a new Anthropologie Accessories store, and BHLDN, the new Anthropologie-inspired wedding brand. The designs for Anthropologie aimed to create an unimagined experience for the customer, which is Anthropologie's mission statement.</p>
			</div>
